# BagBallProblem

In a bag, there are n identical balls (n >= 1) that needs to be removed from the bag.
You can either remove one ball or two balls at a time. Write a code that, 
given n, calculates how many different ways you can remove the balls from the bag.

Programme Output is given below:-
===============================
Input Number of Balls in a Bag: 
asas
